844051","tid":1435331,"uid":30470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"仲有和暢金廚, 今日路過見到老細買咗幾箱水準備聽日派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee58620819ae51f04b425f3181d28de1f366fdc7","tid":1435331,"uid":22121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"未試過加藤屋可以嚟試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺太和商場，近火車站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxvD0uf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxvD0uf.png&h=d391190f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65f583450f7ec5aed95d703b45a3bc6ac97c39d6","tid":1435331,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e574f5df22e47d178014409119b80ed1ecfc0f36","tid":1435331,"uid":285163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1452d9a12a3cbfb72ee6fd1f00bd7537e47e97b","tid":1435331,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d840a2b00bc19015688ccc913ffdd39aa7178f","tid":1435331,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙普選設時限，為港獨正名，不能無了期五大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"5d2d8b10239f11ade06fa8dfb72ad87eb68882e5","tid":1435331,"uid":259374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"記得唔好幫襯大埔街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c7adcdaac7522b6aa379c908dad5c07a301bce","tid":1435331,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162268599295245?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10162268599295245%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4ee10623\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162268599295245?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n新街市熟食，唔歡迎黑衣人"},{"pid":"50b62e0b18b706a10759a353a28af1075d862d9d","tid":1435331,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c63f4035a2f6584a84eda721b7fb0c2353ceef8","tid":1435331,"uid":156914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"昌運雞蛋仔，屌打全港雞蛋仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"難食又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98705b3f655babdcdb05776eab6470a0ac4d4293","tid":1435331,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992df5b469b571610073fe4076c4bc96bdb01b05","tid":1435331,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"去海濱公園個回歸塔賀回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5bdf772a00f92fdceb70eab6a4a93939f7e3c5","tid":1435331,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"想試下大埔中心間好難食<br />\n聽聞係藍絲開"},{"pid":"1e8a33508478212a75